&quot;Considered to be quite a delicacy in many restaurants due to the tender meat, the Thorshu can be found in the colder climates of southern Terra. Also was the basis of Waka Grey, the sidekick from a 27th century children’s show.&quot;  
The model comparison shows the provided model (left) and the game assets model (right).  100mm tall as a whole model, 70mm tall as the sliced model.  
My model needed more supports which is why the &quot;knees&quot; look like they're unraveling at the top.
